item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - John Miles - Sympathy
item.description:
My initial request for this one was in 2021 and it was crickets. I would like to request it again from a new generation of ShareMania users.
I am looking for the unofficial CD release of John Miles' Sympathy (1980). There is one lossy needle drop torrent; I'm interested in the CD release (which I hope wasn't from a needle drop too).
Thank you.
item.author: JBordons
